General.Name: SHAPE Australia Corp Ltd
General.Description: SHAPE Australia Corporation Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the construction, fit-out, and refurbishment of commercial properties in Australia. It also offers new builds, facade restorations, modular construction, and sustainable spaces. The company serves commercial, education, government, retail, and health sectors. SHAPE Australia Corporation Limited was founded in 1989 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
